                <h2>Best Free YouTube to MP3 Converter Online</h2>
                <p><strong>Convert YouTube videos to MP3 or MP4</strong> and download them with Convert The Spire. Our YouTube converter is the <em>fastest, safest, and completely ad-free</em> solution that supports high-quality audio up to <strong>320kbps</strong> and video up to <strong>1080p HD</strong>.</p>
                <p>Convert The Spire is the ultimate <strong>YouTube to MP3 converter</strong> that allows you to download YouTube videos and convert them into audio or video format. Perfect for listening to music, podcasts, and educational content offline on any device. Our YouTube downloader works with regular videos, YouTube Shorts, and live streams.</p>

                <h3>How to Convert YouTube Videos to MP3/MP4 - Step by Step</h3>
                <ol>
                    <li>Go to YouTube and find the video you want to convert and download.</li>
                    <li>Copy the video URL from the browser bar or YouTube's share button.</li>
                    <li>Paste the URL into our converter and choose your preferred format (MP3 or MP4).</li>
                    <li>Select your desired quality settings for the best experience.</li>
                    <li>Click "Convert & Download" to start the conversion process.</li>
                    <li>Download the converted file when the process is complete.</li>
                </ol>

                <h3>Why Convert The Spire is the Best YouTube to MP3 Converter</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>🚫 <strong>100% Ad-Free Experience:</strong> No annoying advertisements, pop-ups, or redirects</li>
                    <li>⚡ <strong>Lightning Fast Conversion:</strong> Convert YouTube to MP3 in seconds</li>
