                    <li>📱 <strong>Mobile & Desktop Compatible:</strong> Works on iPhone, Android, PC, Mac</li>
                    <li>🆓 <strong>Completely Free Forever:</strong> No registration, limits, or hidden fees</li>
                    <li>� <strong>Multiple Formats:</strong> Download as MP3, MP4, or other formats</li>
                    <li>⏱️ <strong>No Time Limits:</strong> Convert videos up to 3 hours long</li>
                </ul>
                
                <h3>Frequently Asked Questions about YouTube to MP3 Conversion</h3>
                <div class="faq-section">
                    <h4>Is it legal to convert YouTube videos to MP3?</h4>
                    <p>Converting YouTube videos for personal use is generally acceptable, but always respect copyright laws and content creator rights.</p>
                    
                    <h4>What's the maximum quality for YouTube to MP3 conversion?</h4>
                    <p>Our converter supports up to 320kbps MP3 quality, which is the highest standard for MP3 audio files.</p>
                    
                    <h4>Do I need to install software to convert YouTube to MP3?</h4>
                    <p>No! Convert The Spire is a web-based converter that works directly in your browser without any downloads or installations.</p>
                    
                    <h4>Can I convert YouTube Shorts to MP3?</h4>
                    <p>Yes! Our converter supports regular YouTube videos, YouTube Shorts, and YouTube Music.</p>
                </div>
